## critical route analysis

- POST /api/media/sign
  - source: `frontend/lib/features/media/data/media_repository.dart`, `frontend/lib/services/media_service.dart`
  - mounted backend route: `POST /media/sign`
  - affects_auth: false
  - affects_media: true
  - affects_payment: false
  - breaks_user_flow: true
  - severity: blocking
  - note: current frontend and mounted runtime disagree only on the public path, not on signer intent

## historical stale claims removed from active critical set

- DELETE /auth/me
  - reason: old scan false-positive; current MVP client only clears local token state on logout

- PATCH /studio/quizzes/{}/questions/{}
  - reason: current frontend update method uses `PUT`, not `PATCH`

- POST /auth/forgot-password
  - reason: current frontend uses `POST /auth/request-password-reset`

- POST /checkout/session
  - reason: current checkout creation uses `POST /api/checkout/create`

- POST /media/presign
  - reason: current Flutter signer uses `POST /api/media/sign`; lesson uploads use studio-scoped upload routes

- POST /payments/*
  - reason: current payments and checkout code uses `/orders`, `/api/me/*`, `/api/checkout/create`, and `/api/billing/*`

- POST /api/billing/change-plan
  - reason: current code does not call this route

- POST /api/billing/create-subscription-sheet
  - reason: current code uses `POST /api/billing/create-subscription`

